Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Galaxy Railways 777...{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}sometimes called the wandering train.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}That is because it is the only train{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}in the Galaxy Railways whose next stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to say nothing of its last stop...{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}is undetermined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Today, as it carries people{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and their various hopes and desires,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777 is running somewhere{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}out in our universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I haven't seen Manabu around lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you talking about? He said he\N{\c&He1e1e1&}was going home to Tabito, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki should just about be done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, he's scheduled to come back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Knowing him, he'll probably sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He would, he would!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Fate Train"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! What are you doing?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As I recall, the train that goes\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to Destiny Station today is {\i1}No. 550.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah, Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Does this train stop at Destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Destiny, you ask? Yes, well, if you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}continue to ride it long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}it may stop there sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well then, please tell me the next\N{\c&He1e1e1&}regular station we're stopping at,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and when that will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The next place we stop\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will be the next station,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and when we stop there\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will be our time of arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm asking you seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And I'm answering you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}After all, this train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is {\i1}Galaxy Railways 777.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Galaxy Railways 777...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Her rails are still being connected,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and her last stop is still unspecified.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The train with the unknown destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I had heard rumors about her, but to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}find out that she's actually running...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am honored to have been\N{\c&He1e1e1&}assigned to duty on {\i1}777.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I have to be back at Destiny today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the fate that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you are to follow, Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, do you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can it be... Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let 'em have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to be like Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and join the SDF. Then I'll\N{\c&He1e1e1&}let you in too, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Together with Subaru,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we'll be a three-man team!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Listen to you! What am I, your flunky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...want to be an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to travel around the universe,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and draw what I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}what impresses me... in this sketchbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once this is full, I'll come back\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to Tabito and become an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's the sketchbook from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You really are good, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Did you give up drawing?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You enjoyed it so much, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everything proceeds according to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter what anyone does,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they can't beat out fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving an emergency\N{\c&He1e1e1&}transmission from {\i1}777.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I have absolutely no idea\N{\c&He1e1e1&}what is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right now, there are only three\N{\c&He1e1e1&}passenger cars connected to the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Transmission from {\i1}777{\i0} has been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Emergency alert status!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}H- Headquarters, this is {\i1}777!{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Requesting all members\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of SDF platoons on duty
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}to mobilize immediately\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to search for {\i1}777.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Unable to determine\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777's{\i0} point of disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Something is disrupting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the order of the universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777 is something that must not yet{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}be lost. Fate must be preserved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, Shula...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}T- this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777{\i0} is being pulled toward a\N{\c&He1e1e1&}planet with extreme gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There aren't any high-gravity planets\N{\c&He1e1e1&}near Tabito. Where the hell are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Attackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm fine the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the fate of {\i1}777,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as well as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All I can do is accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You mean you're just going\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to sit there and die like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If that is my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There are people who did everything\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they could to live, but still died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're just going to accept it\N{\c&He1e1e1&}without doing anything!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I won't allow you to live like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}They aren't in this universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Sure enough, there is{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}someone else's power intervening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But why {\i1}777...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is {\i1}Galaxy Railways 777!{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please break off your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is {\i1}Galaxy Railways 777!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please break off your attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If this keeps up, we'll be pulled in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}by the gravity. Change our course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's no use, Manabu.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}It won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru! What do you mean, it's no use!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Why won't it do any good!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How can you give up without\N{\c&He1e1e1&}making even the slightest effort!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is this how you gave up on the dream\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that you were so fervent about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is {\i1}777.{\i0} Come in,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Send help immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter what anyone does,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they can't budge fate from its rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Whatever you do, it won't do\N{\c&He1e1e1&}any good. You can't alter fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even so, I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I cannot get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Conductor, take Subaru\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the forward car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}R- right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This way, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}W- what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get going, now, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Manabu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Where are you, Manabu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commander, radar is picking up a train
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that could be {\i1}777{\i0} 6000 spacekilos\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the Tabito system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry and get confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Confirmed! There's no mistaking it!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}That's {\i1}777!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}However, the whereabouts of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}her forward cars are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry and assist {\i1}777,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and locate her forward cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's a message from Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, the location of\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777{\i0} has been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She was identified 6000 spacekilos\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the Tabito system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving a transmission\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from Spica Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They've started rescue operations\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for the passengers of {\i1}777.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Spica Platoon.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Rescue of passengers is 80% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The conductor and a number of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}passengers are unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An SDF platoon member that boarded {\i1}777{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}at Planet Tabito is among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We, Sirius Platoon, will head off\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and search for {\i1}777's{\i0} missing forward cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Locate {\i1}777{\i0} at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways Headquarters,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}this is {\i1}777.{\i0} Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A- are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- it's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll be wiped out by those monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're all destined\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to be killed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter how hard you fight, Manabu,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there's nothing that we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru! Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter, Manabu? Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Main power appears\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to have been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once I connect these...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't touch that with your bare hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why are you trying so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777's{\i0} fate has already been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777's{\i0} rails are still being\N{\c&He1e1e1&}laid down. Her destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}her fate is still undetermined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother struggled to survive right\N{\c&He1e1e1&}up to the end. He tried to defy fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't tell me... {\i1}Mamoru-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No. But you're still alive. Are you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}sure you want to give up on everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}even your life,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}all because of the word "fate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you willing to abandon your dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and everything else that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you've left unfulfilled!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Live! Subaru, stand up to them!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Like we did long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Conductor! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}S- {\i1}Subaru-san...{\i0} here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't give up... on... your... dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you... I'm going to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stop! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, has there been any word\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on the missing {\i1}777?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No, there hasn't been\N{\c&He1e1e1&}any word about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it! How could the forward cars\N{\c&He1e1e1&}disappear without a trace!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Open communications on all ranges.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Continue hailing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- This is 777.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- {\i1}Yuuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Requesting immediate assistance.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- That rascal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Requesting immediate assistance.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Requesting immediate assistance.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon is heading to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the point of that transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is {\i1}777.{\i0} Come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Damn... Somebody!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu... Come, raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Supreme Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This has been your fate, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am Shula.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're being contacted by Sirius Platoon.\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}777{\i0} has been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Two passengers have been\N{\c&He1e1e1&}safely recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Subaru, aren't you glad\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we made it back okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, you're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki...san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take care of Subaru, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you, Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hang in there, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good work. I'm glad you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}made it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hell of a visit home, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Sometimes, people attribute the{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}cruelties of reality to fate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}in order to ease their pain,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}overcome it, and go on living.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}However, when they make fate an asylum,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}they lose sight of the future,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the path down which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}they should proceed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So then, that {\i1}was{\i0} you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She is Shula.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She is me, and she is not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki Manabu, at times, I am\N{\c&He1e1e1&}no longer able to see your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even I do not know why that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...nor what it means for our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go on, now... down the path\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}President, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}How many nights have I\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The smiles and tears that{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The joyful light of{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:23:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to be at your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}VIP Train escort duty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The one being escorted{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}is President Drake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My awful father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Next time on Tales of the{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Galaxy Railways, Episode 14:{\i0} "Ties"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}We're going to encounter{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}something at the next station.{\i0}